## Running the App

Frontend is already running at **http://localhost:3000**

To restart the full stack any time:

```bash
# Terminal 1 — keep running
npx hardhat node

# Terminal 2 — deploy fresh contract
npx hardhat run scripts/setup-and-deploy.js --network localhost
```

